| Account Lockout | OK |
| CSRF Protection (global + meta tag) | OK |
| Multi-Tenancy (kein hardcoded org_id) | OK |
| Passwort-Policy (>= 12 Zeichen) | OK |
| Datums-Validierung Booking | OK |
